    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This Adversary stands out amongst others. It does not enter combat until all Minion and Standard adversaries are killed or defeated. When it does, it enters immediately at initiative count 20 and gains a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls with Unarmed and Taijutsu attacks for each Standard defeated by the players and every two Minions defeated by them.</p>",
